  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize move_to_marker_commit upon marker_seen, and stop only when marker_close is active.",
    "Alternate between forward_commit and scan_full_rotate to ensure regular scanning and avoid long straight runs.",
    "Use commit states for forward and rotation actions to enforce persistence and avoid oscillations.",
    "After obstacle detection, escape via rotation or scan before resuming forward movement.",
    "Never allow move_forward directly after obstacle_front; always pass through a recovery or scan state.",
    "If marker is lost, immediately return to scanning to reacquire.",
    "In marker_close_stop, only allow stop as the controllable action to ensure safe task completion.",
    "Exploration is performed via alternating short forward and scan cycles until marker is found."
  ]
